3. Align fasta sequence using MUSCLE and convert to phylip format

4. cat MAF_Filtered.vcf.gatk6262.fasta | grep "Tai" > Taiwan.txt # create list of samples per population

Taiwan.txt
>100-TW20-NTaiw.fq
